𝟮𝟱 𝗠𝗜𝗡 𝗖𝗜𝗥𝗖𝗨𝗜𝗧 - ladder up, and down!⁣
*𝘤𝘰𝘮𝘱𝘭𝘦𝘵𝘦 𝟻 𝘳𝘦𝘱𝘴, 𝘢𝘥𝘥 𝟷𝟶, 𝘨𝘰 𝘣𝘢𝘤𝘬 𝘵𝘰 𝟻, 𝘢𝘥𝘥 𝟷𝟶, 𝘵𝘩𝘦𝘯 𝟸𝟶.. 𝘢𝘯𝘥 𝘴𝘰 𝘰𝘯!*⁣
• 5 burpee⁣
• 10 jump lunges ⁣
• 20 heismans⁣
• 30 line chips ⁣
• 40 mountain climbers⁣
• 50 toe to jump⁣
• 60 bicycles⁣
—————————⁣
follow @desb___ for more workouts and inspo!
